{"id": "1504272778835136553", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "636931095190962176", "author_name": "setsuna6228", "author_bot": false, "content": "ステージの「発掘」は、キラキラしたマスに止まった時にシルバーコアが貰えるイベントのことです！\n取得条件等はないので、初見のステージではキラキラを探しましょう〜！", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T00:02:58.511000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1120778097101389974"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1504268832292733179", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504295553394020536", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1129096201887821844", "author_name": "ugen_22zi", "author_bot": false, "content": "全マス踏む感覚で進むと良いよ", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T01:33:28.389000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1120778097101389974"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1504268832292733179", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504299888031305873", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "結局なにで倒しましたかー？", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T01:50:41.847000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504413318826164334", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "691906331799453748", "author_name": "fuxtuto", "author_bot": false, "content": "すみません。初心者の質問はこちらでいいでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:21:25.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504413417195311264", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "691906331799453748", "author_name": "fuxtuto", "author_bot": false, "content": "カオゼロに飽きたので初めてみたのですが、\n最初のキャラはファイントでいいのかと、どういったゲームなのかを少し聞いてみたく。", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:21:49.309000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504416362422865930", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "初心者質問のスレもあるけど、多分どこでも大丈夫！\nファイントは使い安いからか序盤から持っとくと良いです！\nまぁ、恒常は結構ガチャ引けるからあまり気にしなくても良いかも", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:33:31.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504416855203512433", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "カオゼロほど編成に拡張性が無いですが、カオスみたいな探索コンテンツの難易度が結構高くて主にクリアを目標とするタイプになると思います", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:35:28.994000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504417115573194833", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "あとストーリーを結構重視していると思うので、カオゼロのストーリーを全部スキップしてる私も読み込んでます", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T09:36:31.071000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504425105009279028", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "691906331799453748", "author_name": "fuxtuto", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます。\n無心でガチャを回し続けて返信に気づかず、すみません。\nストーリーがよさげなので今のところ楽しいです。\n今は限定ガチャのようなものが見当たらないので、ぼちぼち楽しめそうでよかったです。", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T10:08:15.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["763468659863584799"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1504416362422865930", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1504429821139357807", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "934325945416966144", "author_name": "poipoi_5151", "author_bot": false, "content": "ワンダ餅って確保いると思います？", "timestamp": "2026-05-14T10:27:00.314000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
